products.name: JBL T460BT
products.description: Introducing JBL T460BT on-ear wireless headphones. They’re flat-folding, lightweight, comfortable and compact. Under the hood, a pair of 32mm drivers punch out some serious bass, reproducing the powerful JBL Pure Bass sound you’ve experienced in much bigger venues. Music and call controls/microphone are placed on the ear cup. And because your music should go where you go, you’ll get up to 11 hours of uninterrupted audio playback on a single charge. Frequency response: 20Hz – 20kHz
